Rochester Gas and Electric Corpsaid 300,000 shares of 8.25 pct preferred stock, series R, willbe offered at 100 dlrs per share plus accrued dividends, ifany, from the date of the original issue.    It said The First Boston Corp &lt;FBC> and &lt;E.F. Hutton and CoInc> are co-underwriters of the issue.    It said net proceeds of the offering will be used to redeemits 10.84 pct preferred stock, series G, which is currentlycallable at 107 dlrs per share and for other corporatepurposes. Reuter&#3;